\begin_layout Subsection
Modules
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Modules are the basic blocks you connect.
 Think of them as individual effect pedals on a pedal board that you place
 and connect.
 There are some modules that process audio, and some modules that you can
 use to control other modules.
 The ability to control modules is the powerful modular / eurorack style
 workflow that differentiates Digit / Beebo from many other systems.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Add a module
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To start, we'll add a delay to the default preset.
 To do this, tap plus and choose delay.
 
\end_layout

