Import reverbs / cabs
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To import new cab or reverb IRs onto Digit, copy them onto a USB flash drive
 in folders called reverbs and cabs for each.
 Then go to settings and tap Copy IRs.
 The files must be 48 kHz wavs.
 
\end_layout

