\begin_layout Subsection
Changing Presets
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To change a preset with a program message, press the floppy disk icon to
 get to the preset screen.
 Tap set list and add preset here.
 The number next to them is what program change message you should send
 to change to that preset.
 This is also the order the foot switch pairs with D and E will step through
 them.
 
\end_layout

